               <person instant="false"><!--donor-->
                  <persName corresp="PRS0000" instant="false" full="yes">Wälättä Maryam is mentioned as the commissioner (ʾaṣḥafiha) on fol. 38ra. Furthermore her name and the names of her father Gäbrä Solomon, her mother Wälättä Giyorgis and her sister Wälättä Mikaʾel are written in supplication formulas. In addition, several other persons are mentioned: Wälättä Yoḥannǝs (fol. 9rb), Ḫirutä Śǝllase (fol. 12vb), Wäldä ʾƎsṭifanos (fols. 12rb, 38ra), Wälättä Tǝnśaʾe (fol. 13ra), Gäbrä Maryam (fol. 16rb), Wäldä Maryam (fols. 16rb, 19ra), Ḫaylä Maryam (fol. 19ra-rb), Ḫarägä Wäyn (fol. 19rb), Täwäldä Mädḫǝn (fols. 38ra, 41vb), ʾabunä Ḫaylä Maryam (fol. 42ra).</persName>
